### Health check
GET http://localhost:8666/api/health

### Create a household member
POST http://localhost:8666/api/household-member
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "dateOfBirth": "1990-01-01",
  "countryOfResidence": "Switzerland",
  "countryOfEmployment": "Switzerland",
  "averageMonthlySalary": 6000.00,
  "currentCash": 15000.00
}

### List household members
GET http://localhost:8666/api/household-member
